The '''LazerLords''' were a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] gang affiliated with the [[Invids]] under [[Leonia Tavira|Admiral Tavira]]. Like the other Invid gangs, they were based on [[Courkrus]] in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], though it can be speculated that prior to this arrangement they may have staged out of [[Nal Hutta/Legends|Nal Hutta]]. A pair of LazerLords were the first pirates attacked by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] in his "Ghost [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]" guise as they attempted to force themselves onto a native woman; following this attack and other dramatic displays by the Jedi, their ranks were severely depleted by desertion. After the demise of [[Shala]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] and the reassurances of Tavira that the problem would be dealt with, the remaining LazerLords began negotiating a merger with the ''[[Red Nova]]'' crew, who also had become too small to operate effectively.

